    <body>
        <p>To achieve this, you can reset the <codeph>page</codeph> counter at each of the topics
      marked as chapters.</p>
    <codeblock outputclass="language-css">*[class ~= "topic/topic"][is-chapter] {
  counter-reset: page 1;
}</codeblock>
    </body>
